        "title": "Welcome to the SmartUrbanity Questionnaire",
        "description": "SmartUrbanity is a European research and innovation project launched in 2025 to support the transition toward more sustainable, accessible, and people-centered cities. By promoting active travel, shared mobility, and integrated public transport, the project aims to reduce car dependency and emissions while improving access for all.\n\n This questionnaire helps us understand your background, daily travel habits, and comfort with different mobility options. Your responses will guide our analysis of mobility patterns collected later through digital tools and participatory activities. Participation is voluntary and anonymous. Your information will be used solely for scientific and educational purposes within the SmartUrbanity project.\n\n https://www.smarturbanity.com/about",
